Hey, check it out!
Guess what I got?

25
00:02:13,366 --> 00:02:14,560
Rhythm?

26
00:02:15,702 --> 00:02:17,727
No. My first fan mail!

27
00:02:19,739 --> 00:02:21,366
"Dear Dr. Ramoray:

28
00:02:21,774 --> 00:02:24,709
I love you and would do
anything to have you."

29
00:02:24,944 --> 00:02:28,471
My gosh! "Your not-so-secret
admirer, Erika Ford."

30
00:02:29,549 --> 00:02:30,538
Oh, wait.

31
00:02:30,884 --> 00:02:35,287
"P.S. Enclosed, please find
14 of my eyelashes."

32
00:02:36,756 --> 00:02:39,850
In Crazy World, that means
you're married.

33
00:02:42,595 --> 00:02:46,827
