Lives. This came to your apartment.

34
00:02:47,066 --> 00:02:48,556
She was in our building.

35
00:02:48,868 --> 00:02:50,199
Oh, my God.

36
00:02:50,970 --> 00:02:52,870
I got my very own stalker!

37
00:02:55,308 --> 00:02:58,277
You are so lucky, I'm gonna share mine.

38
00:03:00,313 --> 00:03:05,250
Joey, remember we talk about good
thing and bad thing. This is a bad thing.

39
00:03:08,788 --> 00:03:10,278
